6.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大活快D邊爐好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同吉野家比邊間垃圾d?"},{"pid":"a91fe2f7425cbd09d8a94159d621a429801ec4af","tid":61742,"uid":5482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:05:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大活快D邊爐好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同吉野家比邊間垃圾d?</blockquote><br />\n吉仔好好多喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要抵D"},{"pid":"b6c2fd7fc2d92f5c53bcdb6f59d940bc57bb234d","tid":61742,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:08:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大活快D邊爐好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同吉野家比邊間垃圾d?</blockquote><br />\n吉仔好好多喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要抵D</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我咁多間都食過曬<br />\n最撚垃圾係吉野<br />\n<br />\n屌你豉油都冇叫咩打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解揀杜文澤因為佢d肉係即&quot;跑&quot;<br />\n好食好多"},{"pid":"9dd79e1fe718f024b0e72fef57b3710a7f37f51c","tid":61742,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:09:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊食ok?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾時<br />\n搵日一齊食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16a0523275bf454795658dcb9118d77c67f25b7","tid":61742,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:11:23.000Z","msg":"跟機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6074ba3f9c341303089720f00986eb6f31581f","tid":61742,"uid":17684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:12:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同吉野家比邊間垃圾d?</blockquote><br />\n吉仔好好多喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要抵D</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我咁多間都食過曬<br />\n最撚垃圾係吉野<br />\n<br />\n屌你豉油都冇叫咩打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解揀杜文澤因為佢d肉係即&quot;跑&quot;<br />\n好食好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n杜文澤未食過。但個樣好似好正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吉仔就差唔多個個星期一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f4cfcdf3c347f603466ba3e58cadbe5f157579","tid":61742,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n杜文澤未食過。但個樣好似好正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吉仔就差唔多個個星期一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我問佢打邊爐有冇豉油佢夠膽死俾壽司豉油我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過杜都要77蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果有酒樓一百頭我會揀酒樓"},{"pid":"ad6551a04606b3053febea61365a54c579f8ad1e","tid":61742,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:19:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n杜文澤未食過。但個樣好似好正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吉仔就差唔多個個星期一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我問佢打邊爐有冇豉油佢夠膽死俾壽司豉油我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過杜都要77蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果有酒樓一百頭我會揀酒樓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但酒樓唔做一人"},{"pid":"54ee51b8cb53e5a84671e566da8bc81da5cd48f5","tid":61742,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:24:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但酒樓唔做一人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下真嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5b190412668f6ae07152b56f4c0388335e5d3b","tid":61742,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:31:09.000Z","msg":"杜汶澤邊爐係正嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}